          </tbody>
        </table>
        <p class="price-card-disclaimer">
          Document preparation only. We do not represent you before USCIS or EOIR. We do not give legal advice on whether you qualify, your defenses, or your strategy — for that you need an attorney. Imverica is not a law firm.
