          </thead>
          <tbody>
            <tr class="price-row-popular">
              <td><strong>FL-100 Simple Divorce</strong> package<br><span class="price-row-meta">no kids, no property — FL-100/110/115 + service</span><span class="price-popular-pill">Most popular</span></td>
              <td class="num"><span class="price">from $349</span></td>
              <td class="num gov">$435</td>
            </tr>
            <tr><td><strong>FL-100 Full Divorce</strong> (kids + property, UCCJEA)</td><td class="num"><span class="price">from $799</span></td><td class="num gov">$435</td></tr>
            <tr><td><strong>FL-300</strong> Request for Order (custody/support)</td><td class="num"><span class="price">$349</span></td><td class="num gov">$0</td></tr>
            <tr><td><strong>FL-150 / FL-160</strong> Financial disclosures</td><td class="num"><span class="price">$149 each</span></td><td class="num gov">$0</td></tr>
            <tr><td><strong>Post-judgment modification</strong> (family law)</td><td class="num"><span class="price">from $499</span></td><td class="num gov">$0</td></tr>
            <tr class="price-row-popular">
              <td><strong>SC-100 Small Claims</strong> package<br><span class="price-row-meta">SC-100 + proof of service (POS-010)</span></td>
              <td class="num"><span class="price">$249</span></td>
              <td class="num gov">$30–$75</td>
            </tr>
            <tr><td><strong>Demand letter</strong> (pre-litigation)</td><td class="num"><span class="price">$99</span></td><td class="num gov">$0</td></tr>
            <tr><td><strong>WG-001 / EJ-001</strong> Judgment collection</td><td class="num"><span class="price">$199</span></td><td class="num gov">$40</td></tr>
            <tr><td><strong>UD response</strong> (tenant defense)</td><td class="num"><span class="price">$349</span></td><td class="num gov">$240</td></tr>
            <tr><td><strong>Restraining order</strong> document package</td><td class="num quote">custom quote</td><td class="num gov">$0</td></tr>
            <tr><td><strong>Small estate affidavit</strong> (under $184,500)</td><td class="num"><span class="price">$199</span></td><td class="num gov">$0</td></tr>
            <tr><td><strong>DE-111 Probate</strong> petition</td><td class="num"><span class="price">from $799</span></td><td class="num gov">$435</td></tr>
            <tr><td><strong>Full Probate</strong> package (DE-111/121/160/221)</td><td class="num"><span class="price">from $1,599</span></td><td class="num gov">$435+</td></tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
        <p class="price-card-disclaimer">
          Document preparation under your direction. We do not give legal advice, choose the form for you, or represent you in court. <em>Cal. Bus. & Prof. Code §§6400–6415.</em>
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
           CATEGORY 5 — Business + add-ons (gold)
           ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────── -->
      <div class="price-card price-card--gold">
        <div class="price-card-stripe"></div>
        <div class="price-card-head">
          <div class="price-card-icon" aria-hidden="true">🏢</div>
          <div>
            <div class="price-card-kicker">California business + service add-ons</div>
